Package com.phasmidsoftware.dsaipg.adt.bqs

Class LazyList<T>

java.lang.Object
com.phasmidsoftware.dsaipg.adt.bqs.LazyList<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the underlying type of the lazy list.
public class LazyList<T> extends Object
Class to demonstrate that it is possible to create a LazyList in Java. NOTE: this does not represent a true lazy list in the sense of the Scala LazyList because this LazyList does not memoize elements. TODO allow memoization of elements.
